title: The.Tuttles.Madcap.Misadventures-SKIDROW
description:
Starlight Starbright Children`s Foundation is pleased to          
announce The Tuttles: Madcap Misadventures, a                     
first-of-its-kind fundraising initiative! The modern Tuttle       
family embarks on a family vacation to the Alamo. Beautifully     
detailed art & sidescrolling action add to the fun. Comic book    
style cut scenes are brought to life by the voice-over talents    
of Hollywood`s biggest names. Get caught up in this hilarious     
arcade adventure that pairs having a good time with doing good!
